h2. Release notes

* *Bug*
    ** [SM-822|https://issues.apache.org/activemq/browse/SM-822] - java.lang.IllegalStateException: component is not owner, with jmsflow and jcaflow
    ** [SM-915|https://issues.apache.org/activemq/browse/SM-915] - FTP poller stalls with threads waiting on PlainSocketImpl.socketAccept()
    ** [SM-1051|https://issues.apache.org/activemq/browse/SM-1051] - servicemix.bat contains unix style environment variables, instead of all windows style environment variables
    ** [SM-1119|https://issues.apache.org/activemq/browse/SM-1119] - Encoding problem in text returned by HTTP-SU
    ** [SM-1124|https://issues.apache.org/activemq/browse/SM-1124] - Message content silently dropped when conversion fails
    ** [SM-1131|https://issues.apache.org/activemq/browse/SM-1131] - Redeployment fails for Geronimo integration
    ** [SM-1132|https://issues.apache.org/activemq/browse/SM-1132] - No clean shutdown of ServiceMix
    ** [SM-1143|https://issues.apache.org/activemq/browse/SM-1143] - Both wsdl-first-sa projects have the same artifactId
    ** [SM-1144|https://issues.apache.org/activemq/browse/SM-1144] - Error in writeDetails method when I need return fault messages
    ** [SM-1145|https://issues.apache.org/activemq/browse/SM-1145] - NoClassDefFound (org.springframework.aop.support.AopUtils) when deploying the Camel example
    ** [SM-1149|https://issues.apache.org/activemq/browse/SM-1149] - the resource path shouldn't include any "target" to avoid being filtered when build the src kit
    ** [SM-1151|https://issues.apache.org/activemq/browse/SM-1151] - LwContainer test has the version number hard coded inside

* *Improvement*
    ** [SM-180|https://issues.apache.org/activemq/browse/SM-180] - Update JavaDoc link on in website template
    ** [SM-810|https://issues.apache.org/activemq/browse/SM-810] - Create single complete ServiceMix Shared Library

* *Task*
    ** [SM-1146|https://issues.apache.org/activemq/browse/SM-1146] - Change servicemix repo url due to the svn relation out of the incubator area


